Revision history for Perl module Games::GuessWord

0.15 Wed Feb  6 17:42:06 GMT 2002
	- cope with case insensitivity
	- wonderful patches by Mark Fowler which add the won, lost,
	starting_chances methods (and tests) to simplify game logic


0.14 Wed Jan  2 15:50:21 GMT 2002
	- created and released first version as Games::WordGuess has
	disappeared from CPAN. As a bonus, it's got a cleaner interface
	and uses less memory



